OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly low cloud will gradually
OL,6,Flift a little, and limited bright or
OL,7,Fsunny intervals may develop, these
OL,8,Fmost likely across eastern areas.
OL,9,FGenerally dry, although there is a
OL,10,Fchance of patchy light rain, mainly at
OL,11,Ffirst. Slightly milder than Friday.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRemaining predominantly dry
OL,14,Fbut also cloudy, although some limited
OL,15,Fclear intervals may occur across
OL,16,Feastern areas. These would then lead
OL,17,Fto patchy mist or fog forming.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
